    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">QBO Plus vs QBO Advanced vs Desktop Premier vs Enterprise.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 24px;max-width:70ch;">An honest comparison of the four tiers most plan decisions come down to &mdash; user counts, cloud access, inventory depth, automation, and industry features. We hold no reseller incentive in any direction.</p>
    <table class="cmp">
      <caption class="sr-only">QuickBooks plan tiers compared — QBO Plus, QBO Advanced, Desktop Premier, and Enterprise</caption>
      <thead><tr><th scope="col">Capability</th><th scope="col">QBO Plus</th><th scope="col">QBO Advanced</th><th scope="col">Desktop Premier</th><th scope="col">Enterprise</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        {%- for r in vsTable %}
        <tr><th scope="row" data-col="Capability">{{ r.cap | safe }}</th>
          <td class="num us" data-col="QBO Plus">{% if r.plus == 'yes' %}<span class="mark-yes"></span><span class="sr-only">Yes</span>{% elif r.plus == 'no' %}<span class="mark-no"></span><span class="sr-only">No</span>{% else %}<span style="color:var(--color-ink-mute);">{{ r.plus | safe }}</span>{% endif %}</td>
